OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FNew Artificial Intelligence road
OL,7,Fsafety cameras have detected hundreds
OL,8,Fof offences in Sussex during the first
OL,9,Fweek of operation.
OL,11,FSussex Police is the latest force to
OL,12,Fuse the technology, designed
OL,13,Fspecifically to detect drivers using a
OL,14,Fmobile phone or not wearing a seatbelt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
