OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FThese are among the 'fatal five'
OL,7,Foffences, and during the last three
OL,8,Fyears in Sussex, 82 people have been
OL,9,Finvolved in a collision where someone
OL,10,Fwas driving whilst using a mobile
OL,11,Fphone, and 214 people have been
OL,12,Finjured in a collision due to not
OL,13,Fwearing a seatbelt.
OL,15,FIn the first seven days of operation,
OL,16,Fthe cameras recorded 620 seatbelt
OL,17,Foffences; 110 mobile phone offences;
OL,18,F17 combined mobile phone and seatbelt
OL,19,Foffences; and one offence of not being
OL,20,Fin proper control of a vehicle (no
OL,21,Fhands on the steering wheel).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FSussex Police Chief Constable Jo
OL,7,FShiner, who is also the roads policing
OL,8,Flead for the National Police Chiefs'
OL,9,FCouncil, said: "We have embraced the
OL,10,Fuse of modern technology not only to
OL,11,Fshow that we listen to concerns raised
OL,12,Fby communities across Sussex, but also
OL,13,Fto help reduce the number of people
OL,14,Fkilled and seriously injured on our
OL,15,Froads through irresponsible driver
OL,16,Fbehaviour.
OL,26,@qD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,F"We know from a previous trial in 2024
OL,7,Fthat seatbelt and mobile phone
OL,8,Foffences are rife on our roads, and
OL,9,FI'm hugely disappointed by these
OL,10,Flatest statistics.
OL,12,F"While the vast majority of people are
OL,13,Fsafe and competent road users, there
OL,14,Fis still a large number of motorists
OL,15,Fwho continue to take risks, and that
OL,16,Fis not acceptable."
OL,18,FThe high-definition cameras use an
OL,19,Finfrared flash to capture clear images
OL,20,Fthrough windscreens, day or night, and
OL,21,Fin all weather conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FThe vast majority of images are
OL,7,Fimmediately deleted in real time and
OL,8,Fnever seen by a human as they do not
OL,9,Fshow a potential offence.
OL,11,FImages which are sent for initial
OL,12,Freviews are automatically cropped and
OL,13,Fanonymised, with vehicle number plates
OL,14,Fand other non-relevant data not being
OL,15,Fvisible. These are then reviewed by
OL,16,Fofficers for processing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FMark Baker, Sussex Police Road Safety
OL,7,FTeam Manager, said: "In the first
OL,8,Fseven days alone, we have seen a
OL,9,Fnumber of people wearing their
OL,10,Fseatbelt under their arm. This is not
OL,11,Fproper usage, as it could still result
OL,12,Fin serious injuries in the event you
OL,13,Fare involved in a collision.
OL,15,F"The data we have captured so far is
OL,16,Fjust a tiny sample of driver behaviour
OL,17,Facross Sussex.
OL,26,@oD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,F"This suggests there is likely to be a
OL,7,Fnumber of habitual no seatbelt wearers
OL,8,Fwho may never have been involved in a
OL,9,Fserious collision and may not think
OL,10,Fthe law applies to them. But why take
OL,11,Fthe risk?
OL,13,F"Our aim is not only to target
OL,14,Foffenders but also to change driver
OL,15,Fbehaviour in the first place. In an
OL,16,Fideal world, we don't want to record
OL,17,Fany offences; we want everyone to play
OL,18,Ftheir part in keeping all road users
OL,19,Fsafe."
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
