PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777543610
OL,3,C700 offences detected in first week of
OL,4,CAI road safety cameras in Sussex
OL,6,FDepending on the eligibility of a
OL,7,Fdriver, the severity and road traffic
OL,8,Foffence, a course may be offered for
OL,9,Fthe non-wearing of seatbelts as an
OL,10,Falternative to a fine or prosecution.
OL,12,FUsing a handheld phone could result in
OL,13,Fa #200 fine and six penalty points,
OL,14,Fwhich could lead to losing a licence.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
